                </p>
                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <a
                        class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        href="#"
                    >
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl"
                            >thumb_up</span
                        >
                    </a>
                    <a
                        class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        href="#"
                    >
